measurements.description:
One hundred fifty-one flowers and 183 buds on 25 upright inflorescences up to 24cm length;
	plant diameter 43cm, height 28cm, grown in 16-cm black scotch pot;
	sepals and petals deep rose, lightly barred red basally; 

	lip saccate, yellow, orange markings; 
	pollen cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline; received AM award 20225320.
